703758f-a.title: Brooklyn: Columbia Street - Sigourney Street
703758f-a.text:
572 Columbia Street, at, adjoining and south of the S.W. corner of
Sigourney Street. Also seen is 49 Sigourney Street, at, adjoining and west
of the S.W. corner of Columbia Street. The buildings concerned are frame.
June 6, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
